OL,6,FYet again the "TV is dead" brigade have
OL,7,Fbeen left confounded. Incredible      
OL,8,Faudiences of up to 17m tuned in to    
OL,9,Fwatch the England women's team's      
OL,10,Ftriumph over Germany on Sunday.       
OL,12,FAnd while the regular audience for the
OL,13,FCommonwealth Games has been relatively
OL,14,Fmodest, it's beaten the average for the
OL,15,Fslots.                                
OL,17,FNobody disputes the underlying trend  
OL,18,Fthough  traditional TV audiences have
OL,19,Fbeen falling and viewers have been    
OL,20,Fturning to on demand services.        
OL,3,CWould more live programming revive the
OL,4,Cfortunes of linear TV?                
OL,22,                                  G1/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
