OL,6,FBut is the trend inevitable? And do a 
OL,7,Ffew recent events suggest a means to  
OL,8,Frecovery?                             
OL,10,FVarious sporting events, the Eurovision
OL,11,FSong Contest and the Jubilee          
OL,12,Fcelebrations all brought in large     
OL,13,Faudiences. These events were all      
OL,14,Fexceptional but they have one thing in
OL,15,Fcommon: they were all live.           
OL,17,FA download can never beat live        
OL,18,Ftelevision. You simply do not know what
OL,19,Fwill happen next. Even the most       
OL,20,Fcarefully prepared programme can take 
OL,21,Fan unexpected twist.                  
OL,3,CWould more live programming revive the
OL,4,Cfortunes of linear TV?                
OL,22,                                  G2/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35003
