PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1662211378
OL,6,FIt would be wrong to imagine that only
OL,7,Fnews, sport or topical programmes need
OL,8,Fto be live.                           
OL,10,FTake a typical week on BBC One in the 
OL,11,F80s or early 90s. Blue Peter, Wogan,  
OL,12,FHoliday, Top of the Pops and Tomorrow's
OL,13,FWorld were all live. That's Life     
OL,14,Fwhile recorded on the day of          
OL,15,Ftransmission  was effectively live as
OL,16,Fit was only edited in exceptional     
OL,17,Fcircumstances.                        
OL,19,FAll these programmes gained an extra  
OL,20,Fenergy and spontaneity.               
OL,3,CWould more live programming revive the
OL,4,Cfortunes of linear TV?                
OL,22,                                  G3/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35004
