PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1662211378
OL,6,FIt's important to distinguish between 
OL,7,Fthe benefits live broadcasting brought
OL,8,Fthese programmes and, say, a low budget
OL,9,Fsoap opera recorded in the studio as if
OL,10,Fit were live with few opportunities for
OL,11,Fretakes.                              
OL,13,FThe best proof that live TV works comes
OL,14,Ffrom two of the most successful       
OL,15,Fentertainment shows  Strictly Come   
OL,16,FDancing on BBC One and I'm a Celebrity
OL,17,Fon ITV. Even Strictly's recorded      
OL,18,Fresults show loses a little of that   
OL,19,Fenergy although the reasons for       
OL,20,Frecording it are valid.               
OL,3,CWould more live programming revive the
OL,4,Cfortunes of linear TV?                
OL,22,                                  G4/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
