OL,6,FBut little shows the energy of live   
OL,7,Ftelevision better than a programme    
OL,8,Fgetting a one-off repeat on BBC Four as
OL,9,Fpart of a celebration of Saturday night
OL,10,FTV  Noel's House Party.              
OL,12,FThe long decline of the show in its   
OL,13,Flater years means it can be easy to   
OL,14,Fforget how special it once was.       
OL,16,FIt was a rare example of a high-profile
OL,17,FBBC programme with absolutely no      
OL,18,Fpurpose other than to try to make     
OL,19,Fpeople happy  even most comedies and 
OL,20,Fquiz shows would claim some other     
OL,21,Fmerits.                               
OL,3,CWould more live programming revive the
OL,4,Cfortunes of linear TV?                
OL,22,                                  G5/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
