OL,6,FNHP started life as the Noel Edmonds' 
OL,7,FSaturday Roadshow. It was recorded the
OL,8,Fday before transmission and gradually 
OL,9,Fgrew into a modest hit over its three 
OL,10,Fyears.                                
OL,12,FThe 6pm slot made it popular with     
OL,13,Fchildren, family audiences and some of
OL,14,Fthe "big kids" who'd watched Noel on  
OL,15,FSwap Shop when they were younger. By  
OL,16,Fthen they'd be students or starting   
OL,17,Ffamilies of their own.                
OL,3,CWould more live programming revive the
OL,4,Cfortunes of linear TV?                
OL,22,                                  G6/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35007
