OL,6,FBut this shouldn't take away from its 
OL,7,Fearly success or the demonstration of 
OL,8,Fthe power of live TV.                 
OL,10,FDo more commissioners and producers   
OL,11,Ftoday need to have the confidence to go
OL,12,Flive?                                 
OL,14,FThose who work in live TV  including 
OL,15,Fjournalists  will always testify to  
OL,16,Fhow it gets the adrenaline going.     
OL,17,FAudiences seem to agree.              
OL,3,CWould more live programming revive the
OL,4,Cfortunes of linear TV?                
OL,22,                                  G9/10
